Package: gkrellm-thinkbat
Version: 0.2.2-1
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Adam Sloboda <ja@disorder.sk>
Installed-Size: 80
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.7-1), gkrellm (>= 2.0.0)
Section: x11
Priority: optional
Homepage: http://people.ksp.sk/~rasto/gkrellm-thinkbat/
Description: ThinkPad laptops battery status indicator for GKrellM
 This plugin displays:
  * power consumption
  * time estimation
  * remaining capacity percentage
  * charging information
 .
 tp_smapi kernel module is required as source of information about battery.
